title: Jane Brody's Good Food Book: Living the High-Carbohydrate Way
description: From the nationally bestselling author of Jane Brody's Nutrition Book comes "the ultimate, reabable, understandable, practical, and useful book on how to live sensibly and well . . . a primer on the new nutrition and weight control" (Craig Claiborne). Contains over 350 recipes.
author: Jane E. Brody
